These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, snooker
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Game   | monopoly | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, coral
1. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Color   | aquamarine | coral |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, boat
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Transport   | boat | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, r&b
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-5::.
